<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <title>
    <%= league %> Live Streams | Watch <%= league %> Games Free on Sportsurge
  </title>

  <meta name="description"
    content="Watch <%= league %> live streams free in HD on Sportsurge. Stream all <%= league %> games online with fast loading, no signup, and multiple working links.">

  <meta name="keywords"
    content="<%= league %> live streams, watch <%= league %> online, <%= league %> free streams, Sportsurge <%= league %>, live <%= league %> games">

  <link rel="canonical" href="https://sportsurge.info/league/<%= league.toLowerCase() %>">

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>

  <nav class="top-nav">
    <div class="nav-center">

      <a href="/" class="brand">Sportsurge</a>

      <a href="/league/nfl" class="top-league">NFL</a>
      <a href="/league/nba" class="top-league">NBA</a>
      <a href="/league/ufc" class="top-league">UFC</a>
      <a href="/league/mma" class="top-league">MMA</a>

      <a href="/league/mlb">MLB</a>
      <a href="/league/nhl">NHL</a>
      <a href="/league/soccer">Soccer</a>
      <a href="/league/cfl">CFL</a>
      <a href="/league/wwe">WWE</a>

    </div>
  </nav>

  <header class="header">
    <h1>
      <%= league %> Live Streams
    </h1>
    <div class="header-border"></div>
    <p class="bold">Watch all <%= league %> games live on SportSurge</p>
    <p class="light">Free HD streaming • No signup required</p>
  </header>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>
      <%= league %> Matches Schedule
    </h2>
    <div class="section-border"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- MATCHES -->
  <main class="list">

    <% if (hasMatches) { %>

      <% matches.forEach(m=> { %>
        <a class="match-card"
          href="/stream/<%= m.League.toLowerCase() %>/<%= m.MatchID %>/<%= (m.Team1+'-vs-'+m.Team2).toLowerCase().replace(/\s+/g,'-') %>">

          <img src="<%= m.LeagueLogo || m['League logo'] %>" class="icon">

          <div class="info">
            <div class="league">
              <%= m.League %>
            </div>
            <div class="title">
              <%= m.Team1 %> vs <%= m.Team2 %>
            </div>
            <div class="time">
              <%= m.Date %> • <%= m.Time %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <% }) %>

          <% } else { %>

            <div class="no-matches-box">
              <h2>No Live Matches Available</h2>
              <p>
                There are currently no scheduled or live <strong>
                  <%= league %>
                </strong> matches.
                Please check back later for updated fixtures and live streams.
              </p>
              <p class="light">
                We regularly update our schedule as soon as new matches are announced.
              </p>
            </div>

            <% } %>

              <section class="article-box">

                <h2>About <%= league %> Live Streams on Sportsurge</h2>

                <p>
                  Sportsurge is a trusted destination for watching
                  <strong>
                    <%= league %>
                  </strong> live streams online in high definition.
                  Fans from around the world rely on Sportsurge to access free live sports
                  coverage without subscriptions, sign-ups, or hidden fees.
                </p>

                <p>
                  Whether you’re searching for upcoming <%= league %> games, live matchups,
                    or today’s full schedule, Sportsurge delivers fast and reliable streaming
                    links. The platform is optimized for both desktop and mobile devices,
                    allowing fans to enjoy <%= league %> action anytime, anywhere.
                </p>

                <h3>Why Watch <%= league %> on Sportsurge?</h3>

                <p>
                  Sportsurge offers a clean and user-friendly interface designed specifically
                  for sports fans. With no registration required, you can instantly access
                  live <%= league %> streams by simply clicking on your desired matchup.
                    This makes Sportsurge one of the easiest ways to follow your favorite teams.
                </p>

                <p>
                  The platform is regularly updated to ensure fans never miss important
                  <%= league %> games. From regular season clashes to high-profile matchups,
                    all streams are organized clearly for quick and easy access.
                </p>

                <h3>High-Quality & Reliable Streaming Experience</h3>

                <p>
                  Sportsurge focuses on providing stable <%= league %> streams with minimal
                    buffering and smooth playback. If a stream becomes unavailable, alternative
                    links are often available to ensure uninterrupted viewing.
                </p>

                <p>
                  Stay connected with the latest <%= league %> action and enjoy live sports
                    streaming without hassle. Sportsurge continues to be a top choice for fans
                    who want fast, free, and reliable access to live <%= league %> games.
                </p>

              </section>

  </main>

 <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="footer-inner">

      <p class="copyright">
        © 2025 Sportsurge. All rights reserved.
      </p>

      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="https://streameasttv.us/">Streameast</a>
        <a href="https://totalsportek.sbs/">Totalsportek</a>
        <a href="https://stream2watch.cyou/">Stream2Watch</a>
        <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="/dmca">DMCA</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </div>

      <p class="powered">
        Sportsurge provides access to live sports streams including NFL, NBA,
        UFC, MMA, Boxing, Soccer and more.
      </p>

    </div>
  </footer>

</body>


</html>
